OL,3,C'Heartbroken' family pay tribute to
OL,4,Csecond man who died following A1(M)
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe family of a 20-year-old man who
OL,8,Fdied following a crash on the A1(M)
OL,9,Fhave said they are "totally devastated
OL,10,Fby this loss."
OL,12,FLewis Smith, from South Shields, was a
OL,13,Fpassenger in a Mercedes A-Class which
OL,14,Fis believed to have struck the central
OL,15,Freservation before coming to rest on
OL,16,Fits roof, on 26 April.
OL,18,FHe suffered life-threatening injuries
OL,19,Fand was taken to the Royal Victoria
OL,20,FInfirmary in Newcastle, where he died
OL,21,Fthe following afternoon.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@NO]
