PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777993872
OL,3,C'Heartbroken' family pay tribute to
OL,4,Csecond man who died following A1(M)
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"Lewis, our beautiful, sparkly blue-
OL,8,Feyed boy; you were your dad's sunnn,
OL,9,Fand your mam's voice of reason. You
OL,10,Fwere the glue that kept our family
OL,11,Ftogether, with a smile that lit up a
OL,12,Fthousand skies.
OL,14,F"We are all heartbroken and totally
OL,15,Fdevastated by this loss. We all love
OL,16,Fyou, son ` you will be missed but
OL,17,Fnever forgotten and will stay in our
OL,18,Fhearts and thoughts forever."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
