PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1777993872
OL,3,C'Heartbroken' family pay tribute to
OL,4,Csecond man who died following A1(M)
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FThe driver of the car, 20-year-old
OL,8,FJordan Orrock, also from South
OL,9,FShields, sustained critical injuries
OL,10,Fand was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,12,FA second passenger, a man also aged
OL,13,F20, sustained serious injuries and was
OL,14,Ftaken hospital for treatment.
OL,16,FPolice are continuing to investigate
OL,17,Fand have appealed for witnesses,
OL,18,Fincluding anyone with dashcam footage
OL,19,Fof the vehicle prior to the collision.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
